      "title": "Algorithm 6 TraceProcessing(T, \\mathcal{C})\n\nInput: A Boolean circuit \\mathcal{C} and a computational trace T = (v_1, \\dots, v_t)\n\nOutput: A new computational trace T' = (v'_1, \\dots, v'_{|M|})\n\n1: M \\leftarrow \\text{DetectCoOperand}(\\mathcal{C}, \\otimes)\n\n2: for each g exists in M do\n\n3: \\mathcal{G} \\leftarrow M[g]\n\n4: v'_g \\leftarrow \\bigoplus_{g' \\in \\mathcal{G}} v_{g'}\n\n5: end for",
